// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-3012 — Mass File Rename (akira)
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 38068b35-4241-5e80-9e68-9f32cf49b992

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
